MKS CORP (3507)  said unconsolidated sales
in April fell 17.03% to NT$30,731,000 from NT$37,038,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  4/2012           4/2011
Sales             30,731           37,038    
YOY%             -17.03%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            101,528          124,964    
YOY%             -18.75% 
=================================================================
 